# Project Idea

A mobile application named "Voice to Text: Communication Assistant" designed to facilitate real-time communication for deaf or hard-of-hearing individuals. It instantly transcribes spoken words into large, easy-to-read text displayed on the screen.

## Core Functionality
- Real-time speech transcription to text.
- Conversation history storage and retrieval.
- Customizable display settings (font size, theme).
- Screen protection mode to prevent accidental interactions.

